<br>
Warrior was swinging two proc weapons.  Fully buffed with Avatar.  <br>
<br>
I was swinging Greatstaff of the four winds, also fully buffed with Avatar.<br>
<br>
No matter what, he could not get agro from me. He'd taunt and mob would whip back around again.<br>
<br>
<br>
He then switched to some crappy bane 2hs (44/46 in POV is what it works out to, no proc)<br>
<br>
He was able to hold agro about 85% of the time, and when I would get agro, he would quickly get it back.<br>
<br>
<br>
Granted, these tests aren't all that scientific (although we had a second warrior show up and verified that he could hold agro lot better with 2hs)<br>
<br>
I'd suggest testing this.. Time to pull out those Twisted Steel bastard swords, see how they do. <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://divineguildpics.homestead.com/files/gartansig.JPG"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><br>
